@NODE "Future" "Stuff still to come"

  @{b}@{u}The Future@{uu}@{ub}

@{b}o@{ub} The first #modulez .mod compo is now on! There will be entries from most,
  if not all, musicians in the group.

@{b}o@{ub} Hyper can't really be arsed to use a PC and get his Jungle XM finished.
  Maybe it'll be released when he gets the new DigiBooster 2 Pro. 

@{b}o@{ub} MaGGoTMaN is off the net due to lack of money. Hopefully he'll get rich
  and get back on sometime.

@{b}o@{ub} Wulf and Chill have been talking about coding a music demo. Hyper will
  be there to give moral support :)

@{b}o@{ub} We're constantly on the lookout for new members. If you're
  interested then send me a mail(preferably with a sample of your work) and we'll
  see what we can do. Most of all we'd like to get a dedicated coder or an 
  artist. We may also be interested in co-operating with other groups, like
  I said, just contact me...

 @{" Main Menu " Link "Main"}  
